# Summary
This documentation details the Batch destination integration for syncing Amplitude cohorts to Batch's customer engagement platform, allowing targeted push notifications and emails. The setup requires paid plans for both services, API keys from Batch, and proper identifier mapping between platforms, with options for syncing to either Batch Omnichannel projects or specific apps/websites.

